      "text": "env:\n  - name: DB_PASSWORD\n    value: \"password123\"\n\nProblems:\n• Visible in git forever\n• Anyone with repo access sees it\n• Even if deleted, history\n  preserves it\n• NEVER do this", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 3,
