      "text": "kind: Secret\ndata:\n  password: bXlzZWNyZXQ=  # base64\n\nProblems:\n• Manifest sprawl: update manually\n  in every cluster on rotation\n• Can't commit to git (GitOps fails)\n• base64 is NOT encryption\n• Doesn't scale", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 3,
